2.title: Vegas Baby!
2.plot: From $3.99 cocktails, a waterslide through a shark tank, a zip line over Fremont Street, to life sized Jenga, travel writers, Jeff Miller and Jason Kessler, take on everything from old school Las Vegas to the fabulous strip.

3.title: Phoenix Rising
3.plot: Travel writers Jeff Miller and Jason Kessler head to Phoenix, Arizona, to see all that the desert has to offer. From the breathtaking desert landscapes to the year round warm weather, Phoenix has something for everyone.

4.title: Ribs & Rock-N-Roll
4.plot: Travel writers, Jeff Miller and Jason Kessler take a trip to Memphis, Tennessee to experience its mystery and charm. From eating BBQ to recording an original song at the famous, Sun Studio; Memphis is a true classic American city.

5.title: Big & Easy
5.plot: Travel writers Jeff Miller and Jason Kessler head to New Orleans to explore a city rich in history, food, art and music, making it a destination the whole family can enjoy.

6.title: Super San Antonio
6.plot: Jeff Miller and Jason Kessler visit Portland, Oregon, to find out if it's truly weird or just plain great; handcrafted beers and roller derby revival to a vibrant restaurant and music scene, the Rose City is one of a kind.

7.title: Weird and Wonderful Portland
7.plot: Travel writers, Jeff Miller and Jason Kessler visit the weird and wonderful city of Portland. From its handcrafted beers to its vibrant restaurant scene, Portland truly is one of a kind.

8.title: Big Island, Big Fun
8.plot: Travel writers, Jeff Miller and Jason Kessler explore the Big Island of Hawaii by air, land and sea. From seeing an active volcano up close to swimming with manta rays, the Big Island of Hawaii is a one of a kind destination.

9.title: Maui-palooza
9.plot: Travel writers, Jeff Miller and Jason Kessler explore paradise on the Hawaiian island of Maui. From surfing, sailing, luaus, ATV tours, to great food and resorts, its no wonder Maui is one of the greatest vacation destinations in the United States.

imdb.plot outline: Jason Kessler and Jeff Miller are seasoned travel and food writers who seek out the new, exciting and most relevant activities in the world's most popular vacation destinations to determine if they meet expectations and live up to the hype. Whether testing a jet pack in trendy Newport Beach, exploring a family-friendly theme park in St. Louis, or digging into a bowl of mofongo at a hole-in-the-wall in Miami's Little Havana, the Advance Team's goal is to help people decide if an event is worth their hard earned time and money.
